{"tha-ap521:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap521:0.2":"Phaladayakavagga ","tha-ap521:0.3":"Sabbaphaladayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap521:1.1":"“Varuno nama namena, ","tha-ap521:1.2":"brahmano mantaparagu; ","tha-ap521:1.3":"Chaddetva dasa puttani, ","tha-ap521:1.4":"vanamajjhogahim tada. ","tha-ap521:2.1":"Assamam sukatam katva, ","tha-ap521:2.2":"suvibhattam manoramam; ","tha-ap521:2.3":"Pannasalam karitvana, ","tha-ap521:2.4":"vasami vipine aham. ","tha-ap521:3.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap521:3.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap521:3.3":"Mamuddharitukamo so, ","tha-ap521:3.4":"agacchi mama assamam. ","tha-ap521:4.1":"Yavata vanasandamhi, ","tha-ap521:4.2":"obhaso vipulo ahu; ","tha-ap521:4.3":"Buddhassa anubhavena, ","tha-ap521:4.4":"pajjali vipinam tada. ","tha-ap521:5.1":"Disvana tam patihiram, ","tha-ap521:5.2":"buddhasetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap521:5.3":"Pattaputam gahetvana, ","tha-ap521:5.4":"phalena pujayim aham. ","tha-ap521:6.1":"Upagantvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap521:6.2":"sahakharimadasaham; ","tha-ap521:6.3":"Anukampaya me buddho, ","tha-ap521:6.4":"idam vacanamabravi. ","tha-ap521:7.1":"‘Kharibharam gahetvana, ","tha-ap521:7.2":"pacchato ehi me tuvam; ","tha-ap521:7.3":"Paribhutte ca sanghamhi, ","tha-ap521:7.4":"punnam tava bhavissati’. ","tha-ap521:8.1":"Putakantam gahetvana, ","tha-ap521:8.2":"bhikkhusanghassadasaham; ","tha-ap521:8.3":"Tattha cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap521:8.4":"tusitam upapajjaham. ","tha-ap521:9.1":"Tattha dibbehi naccehi, ","tha-ap521:9.2":"gitehi vaditehi ca; ","tha-ap521:9.3":"Punnakammena samyuttam, ","tha-ap521:9.4":"anubhomi sada sukham. ","tha-ap521:10.1":"Yam yam yonupapajjami, ","tha-ap521:10.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap521:10.3":"Bhoge me unata natthi, ","tha-ap521:10.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap521:11.1":"Yavata caturo dipa, ","tha-ap521:11.2":"sasamudda sapabbata; ","tha-ap521:11.3":"Phalam buddhassa datvana, ","tha-ap521:11.4":"issaram karayamaham. ","tha-ap521:12.1":"Yavata me pakkhigana, ","tha-ap521:12.2":"akase uppatanti ce; ","tha-ap521:12.3":"Tepi mam vasamanventi, ","tha-ap521:12.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap521:13.1":"Yavata vanasandamhi, ","tha-ap521:13.2":"yakkha bhuta ca rakkhasa; ","tha-ap521:13.3":"Kumbhanda garula capi, ","tha-ap521:13.4":"paricariyam upenti me. ","tha-ap521:14.1":"Kumma sona madhukara, ","tha-ap521:14.2":"damsa ca makasa ubho; ","tha-ap521:14.3":"Tepi mam vasamanventi, ","tha-ap521:14.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap521:15.1":"Supanna nama sakuna, ","tha-ap521:15.2":"pakkhijata mahabbala; ","tha-ap521:15.3":"Tepi mam saranam yanti, ","tha-ap521:15.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap521:16.1":"Yepi dighayuka naga, ","tha-ap521:16.2":"iddhimanto mahayasa; ","tha-ap521:16.3":"Tepi mam vasamanventi, ","tha-ap521:16.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap521:17.1":"Siha byaggha ca dipi ca, ","tha-ap521:17.2":"acchakokataracchaka; ","tha-ap521:17.3":"Tepi mam vasamanventi, ","tha-ap521:17.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap521:18.1":"Osadhitinavasi ca, ","tha-ap521:18.2":"ye ca akasavasino; ","tha-ap521:18.3":"Sabbe mam saranam yanti, ","tha-ap521:18.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap521:19.1":"Sududdasam sunipunam, ","tha-ap521:19.2":"gambhiram suppakasitam; ","tha-ap521:19.3":"Phassayitva viharami, ","tha-ap521:19.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap521:20.1":"Vimokkhe attha phusitva, ","tha-ap521:20.2":"viharami anasavo; ","tha-ap521:20.3":"Atapi nipako caham, ","tha-ap521:20.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap521:21.1":"Ye phalattha buddhaputta, ","tha-ap521:21.2":"khinadosa mahayasa; ","tha-ap521:21.3":"Ahamannataro tesam, ","tha-ap521:21.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap521:22.1":"Abhinnaparamim gantva, ","tha-ap521:22.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap521:22.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap521:22.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap521:23.1":"Tevijja iddhipatta ca, ","tha-ap521:23.2":"buddhaputta mahayasa; ","tha-ap521:23.3":"Dibbasotasamapanna, ","tha-ap521:23.4":"tesam annataro aham. ","tha-ap521:24.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap521:24.2":"yam phalam adadim tada; ","tha-ap521:24.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap521:24.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap521:25.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap521:25.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap521:25.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap521:26.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap521:26.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap521:26.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap521:27.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap521:27.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap521:27.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap521:28.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sabbaphaladayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap521:29.1":"Sabbaphaladayakattherassapadanam navamam. "}